    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from scipy.integrate import solve_ivp\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "c9cc13d8",
   "metadata": {

   "source": [
    "alpha_t = 0.12\n",
    "alpha_s = 0.79\n",
    "gama = 2.8e7\n",
    "tho = 1.32e9\n",
    "tae = 28\n",
    "tap_list = [7, 10] \n",
    "v = 0.4e17\n",
    "fp = -3e-10\n",
    "fe = 3e-10\n",
    "\n",
    "def q_func(tp, te, sp, se):\n",
    "    return gama * (alpha_t * (te - tp) + alpha_s * (sp - se))\n",
    "\n",
    "def system(t, y, tap):\n",
    "    tp, te, sp, se = y\n",
    "    q = q_func(tp, te, sp, se)\n",
    "    dT = tp - te\n",
    "    dS = sp - se\n",
    "    tp_dt = - (abs(q) / v) * dT + (1 / tho) * (tap - tp)\n",
    "    te_dt =   (abs(q) / v) * dT + (1 / tho) * (tae - te)\n",
    "    sp_dt = - (abs(q) / v) * dS + fp\n",
    "    se_dt =   (abs(q) / v) * dS + fe\n",
    "    return [tp_dt, te_dt, sp_dt, se_dt]\n",
    "\n",
    "initial_cond = [10, 26, 34, 36]\n",
    "time_step = 86400\n",
    "nbr_of_step = 500 * 365\n",
    "t_ev = np.linspace(0, time_step * nbr_of_step, nbr_of_step)\n",
    "t_span = (t_ev[0], t_ev[-1])\n",
    "\n",
    "seconds_per_year = 365 * 24 * 3600\n",
    "\n",
    "solutions = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "for tap in tap_list:\n",
    "    sol = solve_ivp(lambda t, y: system(t, y, tap), t_span, initial_cond, method='RK45', t_eval=t_ev)\n",
    "    tp, te, sp, se = sol.y\n",
    "    solutions[tap] = {\n",
    "        't': sol.t,\n",
    "        'Tp': tp,\n",
    "        'Te': te,\n",
    "        'Sp': sp,\n",
    "        'Se': se,\n",
    "        'q': q_func(tp, te, sp, se)\n",
    "    }\n",
    "\n",
    "for idx, tap in enumerate(tap_list):\n",
    "    t = solutions[tap]['t'] / seconds_per_year\n",
    "    Tp = solutions[tap]['Tp']; Te = solutions[tap]['Te']\n",
    "    Sp = solutions[tap]['Sp']; Se = solutions[tap]['Se']\n",
    "    Tp_conv = Tp[-1]; Te_conv = Te[-1]\n",
    "    Sp_conv = Sp[-1]; Se_conv = Se[-1]\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(14,5))\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Temperature subplot (left)\n",
    "    plt.subplot(1,2,1)\n",
    "    plt.plot(t, Tp, label=f\"Tp (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "    plt.plot(t, Te, label=f\"Te (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "    if idx == 1:\n",
    "        t0 = solutions[tap_list[0]]['t'] / seconds_per_year\n",
    "        plt.plot(t0, solutions[tap_list[0]]['Tp'], '--', label=f\"Tp (tap={tap_list[0]})\")\n",
    "        plt.plot(t0, solutions[tap_list[0]]['Te'], '--', label=f\"Te (tap={tap_list[0]})\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Temperature (C)\")\n",
    "    plt.title(f\"T_p & T_e over time (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "\n",
    "    # convergence box (for temperature)\n",
    "    plt.text(0.02, 0.92,\n",
    "             f\"T_p*={Tp_conv:.4f}\\nT_e*={Te_conv:.4f}\",\n",
    "             transform=plt.gca().transAxes,\n",
    "             fontsize=10, bbox=dict(facecolor='white', alpha=0.7))\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Salinity subplot (right)\n",
    "    plt.subplot(1,2,2)\n",
    "    plt.plot(t, Sp, label=f\"Sp (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "    plt.plot(t, Se, label=f\"Se (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "    if idx == 1:\n",
    "        plt.plot(t0, solutions[tap_list[0]]['Sp'], '--', label=f\"Sp (tap={tap_list[0]})\")\n",
    "        plt.plot(t0, solutions[tap_list[0]]['Se'], '--', label=f\"Se (tap={tap_list[0]})\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Salinity (ppt)\")\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Time (years)\")\n",
    "    plt.title(f\"S_p & S_e over time (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "\n",
    "    # convergence box (for temperature)\n",
    "    plt.text(0.02, 0.92,\n",
    "             f\"S_p*={Sp_conv:.4f}\\nS_e*={Se_conv:.4f}\",\n",
    "             transform=plt.gca().transAxes,\n",
    "             fontsize=10, bbox=dict(facecolor='white', alpha=0.7))\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# for q\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10,4))\n",
    "for tap in tap_list:\n",
    "    plt.plot(solutions[tap]['t'] / seconds_per_year,\n",
    "             solutions[tap]['q'],\n",
    "             label=f\"q (tap={tap})\")\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"Time (years)\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"q\")\n",
    "plt.title(\"q over time for both tap values\")\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, tap in enumerate(tap_list):\n",
    "    q_conv = solutions[tap]['q'][-1]\n",
    "    t_end = solutions[tap]['t'][-1] / seconds_per_year\n",
    "    plt.text(t_end, q_conv,\n",
    "             f\"q*={q_conv:.4e}\",\n",
    "             fontsize=9,\n",
    "             verticalalignment='bottom',\n",
    "             bbox=dict(facecolor='white', alpha=0.7))\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "  \n",
    "\n",
    "    \n"
   ]
